snippet.title: Prophecies - The Searing
snippet.description:
This is the cut-scene that gets you out of Post Searing Ascalon. The actual part of the game happens 2 years after the searing.

Playlist is here: http://www.youtube.com/view_play_list?p=B02876EF7A8C111F
